Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Odd] Wow, can he talk!</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>Do we have to listen to all of this?</c.bg_transparent>
