Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>and my devirtualization program</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>will be completed.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Do you think{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}it's going to work, Jeremy?{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Do I have a chance of finally{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}being materialized in your world{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}and becoming somebody like you?{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>I sure hope so. Anyway,</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>there's one thing that I'm sure of.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>I've never been as close</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>to the answer as now.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Oh, honestly, it's so hard to imagine.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}We can be face to face{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}in the same room.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
