Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[computer beeps]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[sighs] I don't get it!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}It's not the end of the world. I'm sure,{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Jeremy, that one day, you'll succeed.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] Aelita, I...</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>I'm beginning to wonder</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>if I'm up to the job...</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>If I'm good enough</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>for such a complicated program.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Sorry. I'm just tired</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>and jumpy, that's all.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>I better go and stretch my legs.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>See you later.</c.bg_transparent>
