Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Uh? Jeremy... Hey, what's this?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Another one of Jeremy's</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>materialization programs.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Oh, wow, candy!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-[Jeremy] Odd!</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-[Odd grunts]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] How many times have I told you</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>not to touch my computer</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>when I'm not here?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-There are months of work in there.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-Relax, Max.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Odd] I didn't hurt your little toy.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Oh, no! You're such a cosmic creep!</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>Now look what you've done!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Those keys are sensitive!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Okay, a little piece of candy</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>is not gonna wreck your keyboard.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] Uh?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>That's crazy!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>This is really mega insane!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[computer beeps]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] Yes! It works!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy laughs] Odd, you're a genius.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>You know that?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Make up your mind.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>Am I a genius or a creep?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] A creepy genius.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>You didn't do it on purpose,</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>but dropping the candies on the keyboard,</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:04:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>modified and relaunched my program.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>I dunno what happened, but it works.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-Thanks, Odd.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-Who's an Einstein now?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-Are you gonna materialize Aelita?</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-Well, yeah.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>The problem is I only get one try</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>and that's it.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Because I didn't see what kind</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>of programming the candy typed in.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Odd] Yeah, so? There's only one Aelita.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Go and tell the others.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>I'll announce the good news to Aelita.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[theme music]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Uh uh.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Yumi, it's now or never.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>We may not get a second chance.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] What if there's a bug?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>I'll never be able</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>to set up the program again.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Listen,</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>you can't materialize Aelita like that</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>without making preparations.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>I've boosted the scans.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>I've got the program going.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-Everything's ready.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-Yeah, in your head.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Hey, come back to Earth, Jeremy.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>Try to be practical for once.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Aelita has no parents</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>or a birth certificate.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>What's more, she's not enrolled</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>in any school. OK, that's no biggie.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>But all that together means</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>she doesn't exist in our world.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Imagine, "Hi, I'm Aelita.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>I come from a virtual reality."</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>That's a one way ticket to the nuthouse.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}You know, Jeremy,{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}it doesn't have to be today. I can wait.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Well, what do we do now?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>I can put her up at my house.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>My folks wouldn't mind.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>And you can plug</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>into the City Hall computers</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>and create a phony identity for her.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Find her a new name... Whatever she needs.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Then you just have to enroll her</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>at our school,</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>and try to put her in our class.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>That'd be really cool, huh?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Okay, we'll get started</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>first thing tomorrow.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[theme music]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy sighs]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy grunting]</c.bg_transparent>
