Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Am I asleep?{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Come on, Jeremy, you know{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}that virtual beings never sleep.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>I can't sleep a wink.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>I can't stop thinking</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>and It's keeping me up.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>You can't imagine all the things</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>you're gonna discover in our world.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}-You mean like sleeping?{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-That's right.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-That and all kinds of fun things.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}-Tell me more.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[snoring]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Odd snores]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-[sinister music]</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-[electricity crackling]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[engines starting]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>When you touch an object</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>with your fingers,</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>you have a sort of sensation.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>It could be a feeling of softness,</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>or of heat, or it could be cold.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Oh, I see. I thought that{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}you only sensed with your brain.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>That's right,</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>but it's a little more complicated.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Here on Earth, everyone has five senses.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:07:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>You, Aelita, only have two of them:</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>hearing and seeing.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}-You can only see and hear.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-Speaking of hearing...</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Soon you'll be able to touch...{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Jeremy, I think I just heard XANA!</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>He's up to something!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[bulldozer engine rumbling]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>What's all that noise, I wonder?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Aelita] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Jeremy,{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}XANA's launched an attack!{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Okay, listen, Aelita.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>Go and hide in a deactivated tower.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>I'll contact you from the factory.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Odd snores]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] Odd, wake up! XANA's attacking!</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>Odd, wake up!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>What was that? What'd you say</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>about carpet tacking?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] Ulrich, get up!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>It's a XANA alert!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Ulrich pants]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Ulrich coughs]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>What did you say?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>I said, it's a XANA alert.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>XANA's attacking!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Do you always sleep</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>with those things in your ears?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, Odd, always,</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>and one of these days I'll tell you why.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Huh?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[theme music]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:08:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[engine rumbling]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[panting]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Odd] No need to look any further.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>This time, he picked a real winner.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>He's attacking us with bulldozers.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>Nice going, XANA. How subtle can you get!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Ulrich] Jeremy, rush over to the lab</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>and call Yumi.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Odd and I are gonna try</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>and stop these monsters.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[panting]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-I'll take the front one.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-Got you!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[grunts]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Oh!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[phone ringing]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Yumi groans]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[phone ringing]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Come on, Yumi, get up. We really need you.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Do you realize what time it is?</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>Bulldozers?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>What bulldozers?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:08:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>XANA's controlling the thing.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what to do, Ulrich.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>That makes two of us. You go</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>and meet Yumi and Jeremy at the lab.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>If I can find out</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>what XANA wants to do with these monsters,</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-that sure would help.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-Okay, just be careful.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[panting]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Aelita panting]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Eyes open, Aelita!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}You never know{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}where XANA's monsters are hiding.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Aelita] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Don't worry.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}No enemy in sight for the moment.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}But the pulse beats are stronger.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}The activated tower can't be too far away.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[grunts]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[yells] Woah!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[elevator zooms]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[hatch buzzes]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Aelita, don't worry.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>Odd should be there soon.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Let's hope that Yumi</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>and Ulrich are on their way.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Ulrich? He's on the bulldozer,</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>trying to find out what XANA's up to.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] Ulrich, do you read me?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Ulrich] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Bad news, Jeremy.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>I'm on the river bank, and I'm afraid</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>XANA's target is the factory.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>That's gotta be it. If XANA destroys</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>our factory,</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>we can say goodbye to our equipment.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>No more computer, meaning</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>no more communication with Aelita.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Don't forget the scans.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Without them, no more transfers to Lyoko.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Odd] And that means</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>total victory for XANA!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Ulrich, listen.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>Odd's just about to go alone.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>So, hurry up!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Ulrich] I'll do my best,</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>but I can't promise a graceful entrance.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Transfer Odd.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[computer beeps]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Scanner.{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[machine buzzes]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] Virtualization.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[buzzing]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Odd grunts and pants]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[grunts]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-Hello, Odd. You're looking stressed.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-I'm okay, Aelita.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>But I never know</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>what I'm gonna find whenever I come here.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Come with me, Odd.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>The activated tower is this way.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Odd] Okay, let's go and check it out.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:12:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[bulldozer engines rumbling]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Ulrich groaning]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Ulrich yelps]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[groans]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Oh, no! Oh!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[grunts and groans]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[loud crash]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Ulrich, do you read me?{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Yumi] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Jeremy?{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Yumi, I've lost contact with Ulrich!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Yumi] </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>{\i1}Where was he{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>{\i1}when you last spoke to him?{\i0}</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Jeremy] He was going to the factory</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>with the bulldozers.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[panting] Right, I'm almost there.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>I'll find him.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[panting]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Aelita] That way.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Odd] Talk about a reception committee!</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Aelita] Usually,</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>roachsters move in groups of five.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[mechanical footsteps]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[mechanical footsteps]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>It looks like the committee</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>is at full strength.</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Odd grunts]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[pants]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[gasps]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[gasps]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[groans]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>Hello, roachsters.</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>Now, which one of you wants to be first?</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-[lasers blasting]</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-[Odd grunts]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>[Odd grunts]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-[Odd grunts]</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-[Aelita groans]</c.bg_transparent>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<c.bg_transparent>-[Aelita grunts]</c.bg_transparent>\N<c.bg_transparent>-[Odd grunts]</c.bg_transparent>
